snippet.title: Build wonders! Planet Nomads EDITOR Intro/Tutorial
snippet.description:
Download. Build. Have fun.

MAC & WIN download: http://www.planet-nomads.com/editor/

We're releasing a free demonstration of the building part of our upcoming sandbox game called Planet Nomads - a game of creation and survival on procedurally generated alien planets.

Follow development news to learn what we have in store for you. Become Planet Nomad.

http://www.planet-nomads.com

https://twitter.com/PlanetNomads

https://www.facebook.com/PlanetNomads

http://www.planet-nomads.com/forums/

http://www.indiedb.com/games/planet-nomads/
